This is a monthly Indian science magazine whose target group is students of Class VII onwards...
SCIENCE PARK gives much importance to subjects like Vedic Maths, Maths Puzzles, Physics/Chemistry/Biology quizzes, and Science experiments Why? What? And How? Objective Jrithmetic, India's achievement in Architecture, Inventions and discoveries, Science IQ, : T hink beyond Text Books, Business Mathematics, Scien??e Career Opportunities, Placement Tests for Engg/Science Graduates etc etc.,
For Domestic/International competitions like lIT/Olympiad students have to prepare at the School level itself that's why SCIENCE PARK focuses on Basic concepts on Science and Mental Ability Test etc.
